    "It is within the multitude of parameters that LLMs encapsulate their understanding of language, enabling them to analyze, deduce, and resolve the challenges presented to them.",
    "In addition to their impressive capabilities, it's important to acknowledge that LLMs are not without their limitations.",
    "One notable concern is the potential for hallucination, where they generate information that is not grounded in reality or might propagate false or misleading content.",
    "We utilised this feature of LLMs in our study to provide them context of cybersecuirty scenarios through prompt engineering.",
    "Hallucination in LLMsHallucination in LLMs is an issue that arises due to the vast amount of data they have been trained on, which may include inaccuracies or biased information, this issue emerges as a result of the model's capacity to generate text that adheres to learned patterns from its training data, even when the generated content diverges from reality [37] and this phenomenon could pose serious risks in diverse fields, including law and medical consultation, potentially leading to disasters."
